AGAINST THIS JUNKER

101
00:07:37,833 --> 00:07:39,125
IS TOTALLY USELESS.

102
00:07:39,208 --> 00:07:41,458
SAVE IT FOR THE REAL TALENT
INSTEAD OF WASTING IT

103
00:07:41,541 --> 00:07:43,666
ON THIS AMATEUR, KYOICHI!

104
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:49,333
- DON'T LET YOUR IMPATIENCE
DO YOU IN, SEIJI.

105
00:07:51,500 --> 00:07:54,750
- MAN, I AM SO PISSED OFF?
IT DOESN'T MAKE ANY SENSE!

106
00:07:54,833 --> 00:07:56,416
