00:08:14,583 --> 00:08:15,541
TO TELL YOU THAT, HUH?

115
00:08:15,625 --> 00:08:16,666
- YUP.

116
00:08:16,750 --> 00:08:18,125
- I DON'T GET WHAT
THERE IS TO SEE.

117
00:08:18,208 --> 00:08:19,916
THERE'S NO WAY THE
EIGHT-SIX CAN WIN.

118
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,416
