119
00:08:21,500 --> 00:08:24,583
THE KID'S GOING UP AGAINST A
LAN-EVO FOR CRYIN' OUT LOUD.

120
00:08:24,666 --> 00:08:25,708
- I'VE NEVER TOLD YOU THIS

121
00:08:25,791 --> 00:08:27,333
BUT YOU'RE A REAL
KNOW-IT-ALL, KENTA.

122
00:08:27,416 --> 00:08:29,083
AND YOU'D ASSUME
IT'S COMMON SENSE

123
00:08:29,166 --> 00:08:31,416
THAT YOUR S-FOURTEEN IS
FASTER THAN AN EIGHT-SIX,

124
00:08:31,500 --> 00:08:34,750
YET IT DIDN'T SEEM TO WORK OUT
FOR YOU VERY WELL NOW, DID IT?

125
00:08:34,833 --> 00:08:37,208
- COME ON, TAKE
IT EASY, KEISUKE,

126
00:08:37,291 --> 00:08:38,625
YOU'RE JUST TORTURING HIM.

127
00:08:38,708 --> 00:08:39,833
THE RACE AGAINST THE EIGHT-SIX

128
00:08:39,916 --> 00:08:41,708
WAS A GREAT LEARNING
EXPERIENCE FOR KENTA,

129
00:08:41,791 --> 00:08:43,583
SO IT WASN'T A TOTAL WASTE, MAN.

130
00:08:43,666 --> 00:08:45,875
- YEAH? WELL,
TOO BAD I DON'T CARE.

131
00:08:48,125 --> 00:08:50,458
THE EMPERORS, OR WHATEVER
THEY CALL THEMSELVES,

132
00:08:50,541 --> 00:08:54,041
ARE GONNA BE IN FOR A BIG
SURPRISE ONCE THIS RACE IS OVER.

133
00:08:54,125 --> 00:08:56,875
TAKUMI FUJIWARA IS
AKINA'S DOWNHILL KING

134
00:08:56,958 --> 00:08:58,750
AND THEY DON'T EVEN KNOW IT.

135
00:09:01,125 --> 00:09:02,500
- THIS IS THE LONGEST
STRAIGHTAWAY

136
00:09:02,583 --> 00:09:04,750
ON THIS ENTIRE COURSE.

137
00:09:04,833 --> 00:09:08,916
IT'S THE PERFECT PLACE FOR ME TO
MAKE A MOVE IF I WANT THE LEAD.

138
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:11,666
- IF YOU GET IMPATIENT
AND PASS THE LEADER TOO EARLY,

139
00:09:11,750 --> 00:09:13,916
THEN IT'S ALL OVER.

140
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:17,125
- DAMN IT!! THAT'S IT!
THIS PUNK'S GOIN' DOWN!

141
00:09:18,833 --> 00:09:21,000
- THAT'S HOW EVERYONE'S
LOST TO THE EIGHT-SIX,

142
00:09:21,083 --> 00:09:22,625
AND THAT INCLUDES MY BROTHER.

143
00:09:22,708 --> 00:09:24,708
- SO IF YOU JUMP AHEAD,
YOU LOSE, HUH?

144
00:09:24,791 --> 00:09:26,625
- GOOD. I WASN'T SURE IF YOU
COULD WRAP YOUR HEAD AROUND

145
00:09:26,708 --> 00:09:28,750
SUCH A PARADOX.

146
00:09:28,833 --> 00:09:30,583
- SCREW IT! I'M GOIN' FOR IT!

147
00:09:35,416 --> 00:09:38,166
SORRY, KYOICHI, BUT "SIMULATION
THREE" IS GONNA HAVE TO WAIT.

148
00:09:41,541 --> 00:09:43,416
I HAVE THE RIGHT TO WIN
THIS RACE MY OWN WAY!

149
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:49,541
- HE'S FAST.

150
00:09:49,625 --> 00:09:51,416
- ( chuckles ) THAT WAS EASY.

151
00:09:51,500 --> 00:09:54,208
TIME TO SHOW THIS KID HOW
OUTCLASSED HE IS.

152
00:09:54,291 --> 00:09:55,958
AS LONG AS I KEEP
THE ACCELERATOR DOWN,

153
00:09:56,041 --> 00:09:58,875
YOU'LL BE JUST A FADING
GLIMMER OF LIGHT IN MY REARVIEW.

154
00:09:58,958 --> 00:10:00,791
