159
00:10:24,666 --> 00:10:27,375
THE TIME I SPEND WITH YOU
MAKES LIFE WORTH LIVING.

160
00:10:29,250 --> 00:10:30,958
I DON'T MIND IF YOU HAVE
A BOYFRIEND.

161
00:10:31,041 --> 00:10:33,083
