164
00:10:38,583 --> 00:10:40,083
GIVING YOU MORE
MONEY EVERY MONTH?

165
00:10:40,166 --> 00:10:42,250
- COME ON, STOP IT.

166
00:10:42,333 --> 00:10:44,291
THAT'S NOT WHAT
THIS IS ABOUT, OKAY?

167
00:10:50,125 --> 00:10:52,583
I'VE ALWAYS LIKED YOU.
YOU KNOW THAT.

168
00:10:52,666 --> 00:10:55,583
AND DESPITE HOW DIFFERENT
OUR AGES ARE,

169
00:10:55,666 --> 00:10:58,083
I ALWAYS THOUGHT THAT
IT WAS PERFECTLY NORMAL

170
00:10:58,166 --> 00:11:00,583
TO HAVE A RELATIONSHIP
WITH SOMEBODY I LIKED,

171
00:11:00,666 --> 00:11:03,458
BUT WHEN I THINK ABOUT IT,
IT MAKES SENSE.

172
00:11:03,541 --> 00:11:06,625
THAT'S WHY YOU WERE GIVING ME
ALL THOSE GIFTS.

173
00:11:06,708 --> 00:11:09,333
NOW BEING WITH YOU
DOESN'T FEEL RIGHT.

174
00:11:11,666 --> 00:11:16,291
- DO YOU LIKE THIS BOY
AS MORE THAN JUST A FRIEND?

175
00:11:17,625 --> 00:11:19,875
- I, UH, I THINK I DO.

176
00:11:21,375 --> 00:11:23,875
I'M SORRY BUT THAT'S ALL
I CAN SAY FOR RIGHT NOW.

177
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,333
- WHAT? ARE YOU'RE KIDDING ME?

178
00:11:27,416 --> 00:11:29,208
HE MADE A PASS
DURING THE STRAIGHTAWAY?

179
00:11:29,291 --> 00:11:32,208
SEIJI'S IN THE LEAD,
GUYS! ( cheering )

180
00:11:32,291 --> 00:11:33,875
- DAMN, I KNEW IT.

181
00:11:35,833 --> 00:11:38,791
- SEIJI'S DRIVIN' LIKE HIMSELF
NOW! HE'S GOT THIS IN THE BAG!

182
00:11:38,875 --> 00:11:40,875
- YEAH, THAT EIGHT-SIX
IS TOTALLY WEAK!

183
00:11:40,958 --> 00:11:42,916
- boy 1: FOR SURE! AND I KNOW
HE MAY NOT LOOK IT,

184
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:44,958
BUT SEIJI HAS SOME
SERIOUS SKILLS.

185
00:11:45,041 --> 00:11:46,583
THERE'S NO WAY HE'LL LOSE NOW.

186
00:11:49,708 --> 00:11:50,750
- DUMBASS!

187
00:11:55,708 --> 00:11:57,791
I WILL GIVE SEIJI SOME CREDIT.

188
00:11:57,875 --> 00:12:00,916
HE'S MASTERED DRIVING HIS
LAN-EVO AT FULL SPEED.

189
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,708
HE ALSO KNOWS THAT
A FOUR WHEEL-DRIVE

190
00:12:02,791 --> 00:12:04,416
HAS TO ENTER A CORNER
AT TOP SPEED

191
00:12:04,500 --> 00:12:07,416
IN ORDER TO SUCCESSFULLY
COMPLETE A DRIFT.

192
00:12:17,958 --> 00:12:21,083
DURING THE DRIFT ITSELF,
YOU CAN ONLY CONTROL THE CAR

193
00:12:21,166 --> 00:12:23,833
BY STEERING WHILE THE GAS PEDAL
IS SLAMMED INTO THE FLOOR.

194
00:12:25,583 --> 00:12:27,875
